text: Noureddine Bentoumi (born 19 February 1972) is an Algerian cross-country skier. He competed in the men's 50 kilometre freestyle event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Algerian male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Algeria Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chamonix
